"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/425079","Ministry of Defence","false","2015-11-09","<p>The liability baseline for September 2015 and the predicted liability baseline for April 2020 are shown in the attached tables. This represents the implementation of decisions made in the Strategic Defence and Security Review 2010 and the three Month Exercise.</p>","Sevenoaks","Michael Fallon",,"2015-11-09T17:12:11.8Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/425079/answer","Biography information for Sir Michael Fallon","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/425079/answer","Ministry of Defence - 14253 - Predicted Liability Baselines.docx","Ministry of Defence - 14253 - Predicted Liability Baselines.docx","14253 - Liability Baselines","14253 - Liability Baselines","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/425079/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2015-10-30","Armed Forces","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, what his Department's (a) 2015 and (b) 2020 liability baseline is for service personnel for each top level budget.","false","Biography information for Sir Nicholas Soames","Mid Sussex","Sir Nicholas Soames","14253"
